data.description: Welcome Home to 5030 South Barton!! All you have to do is MOVE IN! Enjoy all the amenities Lyndhurst has to offer! The perfect LOCATION; close to shopping, restaurants, and entertainment. This 4 bed, 2 bath, 1.5 story, 1,400+ sq/ft Cape Cod is a MUST SEE & A RARE FIND in this market. MOVE IN READY with enough space for all your families needs. This home has been meticulously cared for with special attention paid to all the details! The home is equipped with two first floor bedrooms, updated bathroom, updated sun room, formal dining room, living room with large windows providing the best sunlight, and gorgeous hard wood floors throughout, the finished upstairs offers two bedrooms with plenty of closet space with room for all your bedroom furniture.  The basement is partially finished with a full bathroom and awaiting your final touches.  This home is situated on over 8,000 sq/ft which allows for a large fenced backyard for all your families activities and entertainment, a shed for your storage & a back up generator. Schedule your private showing today as this one won't last long!
